author: julianfoad
msg: On the 'move-tracking-2' branch: Improve the 'svnmover diff' code
organization.
The only functional change is that paths printed by svn_branch_diff() are
now relative to the specified subtree instead of relative to the branch
root.
* subversion/svnmover/svnmover.c
(diff_item_t): Replace some fields intended for display with more basic
data.
(subtree_diff): New, extracted from svn_branch_diff().
(diff_ordering): Adjust to use the new contents of diff_item_t.
(svn_branch_diff): Call subtree_diff() to get the basic data. When
formatting data for display, don't refer directly to the branch objects as
much as we did before: get most data from the result of subtree_diff().
